Text: Mate, the world’s gone mad.
The Great Barrier Reef's struggling for airtime while everyone’s arguing over who gets to wear the party hats at the climate summit.
Germany's still trying to keep it all orderly while France is waving its arms like a madman over “green” rules.

Meanwhile, the US thinks it’s still the 80s, blasting rock music and kicking up dust without a care, leaving us all dodging back-to-back heat waves and debates about whether to “bring back the thongs.
” On the upside, Canada popped in for a beer and we agreed that camping might just solve everything.
Just gotta watch out for wildlife getting drunk on our cold tinnies!
